# Optional configuration for PDDL Playground.
# Copy to ".env" (or set in your build environment) to enable features.

# URL of the epistemic-planning backend (Phase 2). When set at BUILD time, the
# epistemic (PDKBDDL) examples gain a "Solve on server" button that calls the
# pdkb-epistemic service. Leave UNSET for a fully-offline build (epistemic mode
# stays explain-only).
#   VITE_EPISTEMIC_API=https://epistemic.yourdomain.com
